    tutorialSteps: [
      { text: { zh: '司马炎：为什么要算平均数？\n天下初定，各郡贫富不一。平均数告诉你"如果均匀分配，每个郡能分到多少"。\n这是治国决策最基本的数据！', en: 'Sima Yan: "Why calculate the mean?\nThe realm is newly unified, prefectures vary in wealth. The mean tells you \'if evenly distributed, how much each gets\'.\nThis is the most basic data for governance!"' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '司马炎：平均数公式\n$$\\bar{x} = \\frac{\\text{所有数据之和}}{\\text{数据个数}}$$\n先加，再除。就这么简单！', en: 'Sima Yan: "Mean formula\n$$\\bar{x} = \\frac{\\text{sum of all values}}{\\text{number of values}}$$\nAdd first, then divide. That simple!"' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '司马炎：第一步——求和\n把所有郡的粮产加起来。', en: 'Sima Yan: "Step 1 — find the sum\nAdd up all prefectures\' grain yields."' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '司马炎：第二步——除以个数\n总和 ÷ 郡的数量 = 平均粮产。', en: 'Sima Yan: "Step 2 — divide by count\nTotal ÷ number of prefectures = average yield."' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '司马炎：答案\n全国平均粮产确认！天下大势，分久必合。', en: 'Sima Yan: "Answer\nNational average yield confirmed! The realm united at last."' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '司马炎：验算\n平均数 × 个数 应该等于总和 ✓', en: 'Sima Yan: "Verify\nMean × count should equal the sum ✓"' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
    ],
